    <h1>COVID-19 - Coronavirus Information</h1>
<h3 id="pageTitle"><a href="https://www.edcgov.us/County%20Press%20Releases/Pages/El-Dorado-County-Public-Health-Officer-Extends-Shelter-in-Place-Directive.aspx">El Dorado County Public Health Officer Extends Shelter in Place Directive</a></h3>
<h3><a href="https://bit.ly/3aCLEij">Message to El Dorado County: School Closure Extension</a></h3>
<h3><a title="El Dorado County Public Health COVID-19 update page" href="https://www.edcgov.us/Government/hhsa/Pages/EDCCOVID-19.aspx" target="_blank">UPDATE: El Dorado County COVID-19 Status</a></h3>
<p>The El Dorado County Office of Education collaborates regularly with our county health department and state officials to ensure that county-wide programs and school districts remain informed and have the resources needed to help maintain healthy learning environments. Schools are taking proactive steps to prevent the spread of any illness, including increased cleaning protocols and reinforcing proper hygiene practices.</p>
