<li>
<a title="CA Department of Public Health COVID-19 Update page" href="https://www.cdph.ca.gov/Programs/CID/DCDC/Pages/Immunization/nCOV2019.aspx" target="_blank">California Department of Public Health</a> -<strong> </strong>Official COVID-19 information and Guidance Documents from the State of California</li>
